org.mapsforge.map.reader

Class MapDatabase

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mapsforge.map.reader.MapDatabase

  • public class MapDatabase
extends Object
    A class for reading binary map files.

    This class is not thread-safe. Each thread should use its own instance.

    See Also:
